<subSubSection id="28FB6564FFD0D65E0F3AF34E16BE3B78" pageId="6" pageNumber="697" type="reference_group">
<emphasis id="5295EAFDFFD0D65E0F3AF34E17243ADA" box="[1392,1547,3234,3267]" pageId="6" pageNumber="697">Taxonomy.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="A7E14D6CFFD0D65E0C50F34E16023ADA" authorityName="Tomes" authorityYear="1858" box="[1562,1837,3234,3267]" class="Mammalia" family="Miniopteridae" genus="Miniopterus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="697" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="australis">Miniopterus australis</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicName id="A7E14D6CFFD0D65E0D72F34E19063ADA" authority="Revilliod" authorityName="Revilliod" authorityYear="1914" box="[1848,2089,3234,3267]" class="Mammalia" family="Miniopteridae" genus="Miniopterus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="697" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="robustior">robustior Revilliod</taxonomicName>
in Sarasin &amp; Roux, 1914, “Iles Loyalty [= Loyalty Islands]: Lifou [
<collectingCountry id="18F6767FFFD0D65E0D6AF32516513AF3" box="[1824,1918,3273,3306]" name="Iceland" pageId="6" pageNumber="697">Island</collectingCountry>
], Quépénéé.” 
<taxonomicName id="A7E14D6CFFD0D65E0F3BF31C17AA3B08" authorityName="Revilliod" authorityYear="1914" box="[1393,1669,3312,3345]" class="Mammalia" family="Miniopteridae" genus="Miniopterus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="697" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="robustior">Miniopterus robustior</taxonomicName>
was originally described as a “giant” subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="A7E14D6CFFD0D65E0301F31C18C83B08" authorityName="Tomes" authorityYear="1858" box="[2379,2535,3312,3345]" class="Mammalia" family="Miniopteridae" genus="Miniopterus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="698" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="australis">M. australis</taxonomicName>
, but cranial characteristics clearly point to a distinct species and a diminutive member of the 
<taxonomicName id="A7E14D6CFFD0D65E0FE2F2AC17343B78" authorityName="Waterhouse" authorityYear="1845" box="[1448,1563,3392,3425]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="697" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="tristis">M. tristis</taxonomicName>
species group. Monotypic.
</subSubSection>
</paragraph>
<subSubSection id="28FB6564FFD0D65E0F3AF28B19B03B91" box="[1392,2207,3431,3464]" pageId="6" pageNumber="697" type="distribution">
